releases.body:
- Generate CSS map files
- Entu to Yaml helper script

**All planned v1 features are now done!**

Changes from last release are:
- Delete obsolete build files with _cleanup_ build parameter
- Config file changes
Removed assets copy from build.js (do it yourself!)
External data Yaml files handling changed! Now it's possible to add custom data files from other folders.

Use front matter for page data
Property page.redirect renamed to page.originalPath
Unified action buttons (in desktop app)

Combine and generates _style.css_ from all .styl files (not just style.styl)
Combine and generates  _script.js_ from all .js files
Get custom data from Yaml files if set in _page.data.files_ parameter

Removed basePath config parameter
Added page.disabled parameter
Error notifications and count on app badge

Added menus
Changed keyboard shortcuts for reload (Cmd+R) and inspector (Cmd+Opt+I)
HTML minify fix

Use global.yaml to load global data (available in all jade files in G object)
Internal changes and fixes

Page config parameters _page.redirect_ and _page.aliases_ now work
Open last config.yaml on start
Start server only when needed
Log view enhancements
Reload app with F5 and open inspector with F12
Use random port if not set in config
Watch Jade dependencies (and rebuild pages if needed)
Use page.path for page build folder (You can have different url in different languages for same page)
